articles.title: Fort Stewart Army sergeant in custody after he shot 5 soldiers, officials say
articles.description: An Army sergeant at Fort Stewart is in custody after shooting five other soldiers, according to officials [3, 5].

articles.title: Trump plans 100% tariff on computer chips, unless companies build in US
articles.description: President Trump is considering imposing a 100% tariff on computer chips if companies do not build them in the United States [3, 5].

articles.title: Texas Democrats plea for donations to extend their walkout and block Trump's redistricting plan
articles.description: Texas Democrats are requesting donations to prolong their walkout in an effort to obstruct President Trump's redistricting plan [3].
